description: After a hard day of work out in the field, Brandon Lewis is ready to kick back, relax and have a beer. When he gets back to the garage, he realizes how dirty he has gotten, but also how worked up he is. Nursing a beer and a boner, Brandon decides to honor both, so he looks around and leans back in the only place that seems accommodating: the wheelbarrow. Watch as Brandon strips down, rubbing himself all the while in anticipation of climax. Can the wheelbarrow handle his load? We'll see.Enjoy!
title: Brandon Lewis
